{"tid":1725814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[革命都要有底線]抗爭十誡討論區","createTime":"2019-11-16T01:27:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T02:09:13.000Z","uid":130385,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"22598e190259e9804ccd4555d3d9ea9f27b59841","tid":1725814,"uid":130385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:27:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1725122/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1725122/page/1</a><br />\n睇過小弟的原POST都知  家下港共想係香港攪多次六七暴動<br />\n對家藍絲已經準備好一切卑鄙手段去陷害我地  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話支持五大訴求之後周街打大肚婆   話係手足之後同你清路障比黑警<br />\n偷細路粒糖然後自稱勇武派  偷阿婆底褲之後話自己係黃絲  <br />\n藍絲豪無血性  面皮厚  任何惡行都做得出<br />\n我地再唔制定一套必須遵守的法規  就會好似佢地當年咁民意逆轉變過街老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一人分享幾個認為需要遵守的守則  本人認為十誡幾好  一來有意思  二來可以儲夠10個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e21557cd6b481bb9a544120a8b987263a145190","tid":1725814,"uid":130385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64fa1d05d9555e89bc741850e35ccc2bd47cce03","tid":1725814,"uid":130385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079233853f9c92b71eab6b1c9fb847d5e4b51024","tid":1725814,"uid":130385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd7fc64f31e4aa4dd473d97920665370d8ac5a1","tid":1725814,"uid":130385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T01:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e91009cdd673d2e5f592f1a80cdc05e4b3a04a","tid":1725814,"uid":130385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1